'''藍旗海灘'''是[[環境教育基金會|環境教育基金會]]認可的一種[[海灘|海灘]]或[[碼頭|碼頭]]。<ref>{{cite web |author=Bysted A/S |url=http://www.fee-international.org/ |title=FEE - Foundation for Environmental Education |publisher=Fee-international.org |date= |accessdate=2010-05-21 |archive-date=2006-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060831194457/http://www.fee-international.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.blueflag.org |title=Blue Flag Programme |publisher=Blueflag.org |date= |accessdate=2010-05-21 |archive-date=2008-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080529165244/http://www.blueflag.org/blueflag |dead-url=yes }}</ref>其評選標準包括水質、環境教育信息、服務和一般的[[環境管理|環境管理]]標準，藍旗海灘的各項水準都應高於一般的海灘。環境教育基金會每年6月5日都會發佈重新評選藍旗海灘名單，其分佈遍及全球。<ref>[http://www.blueflag.org/Menu/Blue+Flag+beaches%2fmarinas Blue Flag beaches/marinas] {{Wayback|url=http://www.blueflag.org/Menu/Blue+Flag+beaches%2fmarinas |date=20130911195743 }}. Retrieved 11 February 2010.</ref>2013年共有3850個藍旗海灘，分佈於48個國家。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.blueflag.org/Menu/Blue+Flag+beaches%2fmarinas |title=Blueflag.org |access-date=2014-03-12 |archive-date=2013-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911195743/http://www.blueflag.org/Menu/Blue+Flag+beaches%2fmarinas |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

